## Suggestion

- Update the migration policy in `.specs/migrations_spec` to reflect the actual practice of using incremental migration files, or consolidate all schema changes into the original files as per the current policy.

## Priority

- High (Documentation and migration practices must align to avoid confusion and potential deployment issues.)

## Next Steps

1. Decide on a single migration strategy:

- If incremental migrations are preferred, update `.specs/migrations_spec` to document this.
- If single-file/idempotent migrations are required, merge all changes into the original files and remove the incremental ones.

2. Communicate the chosen strategy to all contributors.
3. Update onboarding and developer docs to match.
